OL,3,CFormer rail worker converts part of
OL,4,Chis home into library
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, Paul said he
OL,7,Fwanted his collection to be
OL,8,F"accessible" to all.
OL,10,F"Rather than just have them here for
OL,11,Fme, very occasionally, to look at - if
OL,12,Fever in some cases," he said.
OL,14,F"Just throw it open to people, so
OL,15,Fpeople can come and use it."
