OL,3,CFormer rail worker converts part of
OL,4,Chis home into library
OL,6,FThe library will be open by
OL,7,Fappointment and for general visiting
OL,8,Fonce a month. He's also hoping to host
OL,9,Fregular talks on the history of
OL,10,Frailways.
OL,12,FPaul has ambitions to do more with his
OL,13,Fcollection - ultimately, he'd like to
OL,14,Fcatalogue all his books online so they
OL,15,Fcan be a useful resource to
OL,16,Fresearchers and enthusiasts alike.
OL,18,F"If somebody wants to come and do
OL,19,Fresearch then they can come by and
OL,20,Fhave a look through the collection on
OL,21,Fsite," Paul said.
